   + do not call INTERNAL SearchDirs() API when compiling base script
     since we have already validated its path earlier
   + Use stat(_) type shortcut for stat() &#38; -X calls where possible
   + Moved @INC initilization up to handler() &#38; consolidated with $INCDir lib
