<dt><a name='VERSION'></a><a name="$VERSION_=_2.29;_$DATE=&#34;11/19/2001&#34;;"
>$VERSION = 2.29; $DATE=&#34;11/19/2001&#34;;</a></dt>

<dd>
<pre class="sh_perl"> +Added some extra help text to the ./cgi/asp --help message
